WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.666 --> 00:00:02.300
Imperial edict arrives.

2
00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:10.366
By the grace of Heaven, the Emperor decrees: Su Shi's daughter, Qingyu,

3
00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:11.966
is of virtuous conduct,

4
00:00:11.966 --> 00:00:13.433
and is prudent and careful.

5
00:00:13.566 --> 00:00:16.166
She is officially appointed as Consort Rong.

6
00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.466
She is granted residence in the Changchun Palace.

7
00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:20.100
Heavenly blessings.

8
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:22.400
I understand.

9
00:00:24.166 --> 00:00:26.433
I hope Consort Rong will be more impressive.

10
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.700
The stage has been set.

11
00:00:28.766 --> 00:00:30.666
There’s no reason for the performance to fail.

12
00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:32.833
George is a cunning name.

13
00:00:33.133 --> 00:00:37.000
With your help, I believe I can defeat Consort Yan.

14
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:38.766
I hope so.

15
00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:52.233
Go back.

16
00:00:54.166 --> 00:00:57.666
Why? Why is it Su Qiuyu, that despicable person?

17
00:00:58.566 --> 00:00:59.666
I am unwilling.

18
00:01:01.066 --> 00:01:02.700
Ah, ah!

19
00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.466
Ah!

20
00:01:11.166 --> 00:01:14.933
Who is that? That’s Consort Rong’s younger sister.

21
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:17.900
The selection failed. The Emperor was angry and had her beaten with twenty lashes.

22
00:01:17.966 --> 00:01:19.400
The second master has been crippled since then. Hmph.

23
00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:22.633
Well, when one feels sleepy, someone hands a pillow.

24
00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:25.600
Find a way to keep this person.

25
00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:28.066
This palace will have great use for her in the future.

26
00:01:47.866 --> 00:01:49.766
The Changchun Palace is being set up in a hurry.

27
00:01:49.933 --> 00:01:53.366
If anything is missing, let Biyuan fetch it from the inner court.

28
00:01:58.866 --> 00:02:01.366
Don’t move. The Emperor seems off.

29
00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:04.166
Could it be that he is attracted to my beauty?

30
00:02:04.466 --> 00:02:06.633
Your Majesty, it’s daytime.

31
00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:09.766
So what if it’s daytime?

32
00:02:09.766 --> 00:02:13.466
Daytime. Daytime is not for that kind of thing.

33
00:02:13.466 --> 00:02:14.600
What kind of thing?

34
00:02:15.066 --> 00:02:16.433
What kind of thing?

35
00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:21.600
Don’t be afraid. I am not that reckless a person.
